25:46.940 --> 25:50.068
is there anybody you know...

25:50.110 --> 25:52.101
who would want
to hurt your grandfather?

25:52.150 --> 25:54.141
No.

25:54.180 --> 25:55.374
Everybody loved him.

25:55.420 --> 25:59.049
He was like a father to half
the kids in the neighborhood.

25:59.090 --> 26:00.648
He...

26:00.690 --> 26:03.727
had such a good heart.

26:05.760 --> 26:07.182
What about Johnny?

26:07.230 --> 26:10.893
No.

26:10.930 --> 26:13.694
