my grandfather

27:14.830 --> 27:18.129
that we were together.

27:18.170 --> 27:19.922
And that we were
gonna get married.

27:23.340 --> 27:26.366
We were gonna try again.

27:26.410 --> 27:28.776
To start a family.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.979
So that's why Johnny
was so distracted

27:39.020 --> 27:40.214
