28:04.050 --> 28:07.042
It came from
a Beretta 92FS.

28:07.080 --> 28:10.117
You know who packs
a Beretta 92FS?

28:10.150 --> 28:13.881
AK's bodyguard,
Mr. Parker.

28:17.390 --> 28:19.950
Johnny tell you
he was quitting boxing

28:19.990 --> 28:21.389
and going into business
with Casey?

28:21.430 --> 28:22.920
He did.
And you didn't think

28:22.960 --> 28:25.428
to mention that
back at Major Crimes?
No.

28:25.470 --> 28:27.062
Johnny wanted to quit
the pro circuit

28:27.100 --> 28:28.260
every five minutes.

28:28.300 --> 28:29.267
He called it a circus.

28:29.300 --> 28:30.289
