28:39.150 --> 28:40.378
Good memory.

28:40.410 --> 28:42.310
I stand by that.
Well, then,

28:42.350 --> 28:44.409
you should be
happy to hear that he's dead;

28:44.450 --> 28:46.247
shot right through
the heart.

28:46.290 --> 28:47.882
Whoa. Uh, not that way.

28:47.920 --> 28:49.785
Not retire permanently.

28:49.820 --> 28:51.026
Really?

28:51.060 --> 28:53.028
Last month, you set up
a $40 million fight

28:53.060 --> 28:54.357
