get to the point.

29:02.040 --> 29:04.031
Here's the point:
we think you had

29:04.070 --> 29:05.833
Mr. Parker kill Johnny.

29:05.870 --> 29:07.531
Then you had him kill Casey.
You were in Vegas yesterday,

29:07.570 --> 29:09.777
but we checked
your plane's manifest.

29:09.810 --> 29:11.243
Mr. Parke_r
wasn't on It.

29:11.280 --> 29:12.349
He never left the city.

29:12.380 --> 29:13.347
