34:45.550 --> 34:46.744
so your alibi is golden.

34:46.780 --> 34:49.248
I mean,
you're a smart guy, Bobby.

34:51.220 --> 34:53.745
I don't know what
you're talking about.

34:55.790 --> 34:57.655
Johnny was supporting you,
