34:57.690 --> 35:00.625
Which is... which is
what a brother should do.

35:00.660 --> 35:03.128
But it's weird, because
we looked into his financials,

35:03.160 --> 35:04.593
and about a month ago,

35:04.630 --> 35:09.135
the checks he was
sending you-- they stopped.

35:09.170 --> 35:11.764
He was cutting you off,
wasn't he?

35:11.810 --> 35:14.506
Yeah.

35:14.540 --> 35:16.804
Yeah, I begged him.

35:16.840 --> 35:18.899
I told him I just needed
a little more time

35:18.950 --> 35:21.919
to get on my feet.

35:21.950 --> 35:23.679
But he said no.

35:23.720 --> 35:28.180
You begged you brother for help,
and he said no?

35:30.220 --> 35:32.552
Look, that's why
I went to the festival--

35:32.590 --> 35:34.729
to-to talk with him.

35:34.760 --> 35:38.218
But he wouldn't listen.

35:38.270 --> 35:40.329
So I hit him.

35:40.370 --> 35:43.464
And he didn't
hit you back, did he?

35:43.500 --> 35:44.831
No, no.

35:44.870 --> 35:47.304
And I'm thinking, "What?

35:47.340 --> 35:48.898
What, I'm"

35:48.940 --> 35:50.009
Like, my baby
brother thinks

35:50.040 --> 35:52.508
that I'm some kind of schmuck
that he doesn't even

35:52.550 --> 35:54.370
need to put his hands up?
Like I'm nothing?

35:54.420 --> 35:57.617
So you hit him again and again
to get him to hit you back,

35:57.650 --> 36:00.483
to get him to fight.
Right?

36:00.520 --> 36:02.408
I-I don't know. I guess so.

36:02.460 --> 36:04.781
I didn't mean
to kill him.

36:04.830 --> 36:05.888
I'm sorry.

36:05.930 --> 36:08.455
I didn't mean to.

36:08.500 --> 36:10.559
That might not do it.
Doesn't matter.

36:10.600 --> 36:12.329
He was drunk, they're fighting.

36:12.370 --> 36:14.736
Most he gets is manslaughter
for the brother.

36:14.770 --> 36:16.829
And Johnny's a fighter.
Bobby may walk on self-defense.

36:16.870 --> 36:19.407
AL: Which is why we need
to get him for the trainer.

36:19.440 --> 36:21.328
Carrie have enough?

36:21.380 --> 36:23.302
