36:33.450 --> 36:35.259
What did you think of Casey?

36:37.620 --> 36:41.226
You know, I wanted
to train with Casey.

36:41.260 --> 36:42.352
See, I was there first.

36:42.400 --> 36:45.995
I was sweeping up that gym
when I was ten years old.

36:46.030 --> 36:46.860
Wow.

36:46.900 --> 36:49.835
And what then?
He

36:49.870 --> 36:52.361
Yeah. Casey saw Johnny...

36:52.410 --> 36:54.571
it's like I never existed.

36:54.610 --> 36:56.703
And the two of them
just cut you out?

36:56.740 --> 36:57.968
Yeah.

36:58.010 --> 37:00.877
I mean, Casey wouldn't
even let me into the gym

37:00.910 --> 37:03.470
to watch my brother box.

37:03.520 --> 37:05.909
You know those gyms
that-that Johnny and Casey

37:05.950 --> 37:07.713
were gonna
build together?
Yeah.

37:07.750 --> 37:10.719
So, I asked my brother,
IIC

37:10.760 --> 37:13.854
Can I get a piece
of something?"

37:13.890 --> 37:16.552
And before he can
even answer me,

37:16.600 --> 37:18.568
Casey's there saying,
"No. No, no, no.

37:18.600 --> 37:20.568
It-it's time to
cut him off."

37:20.600 --> 37:21.794
That I was a parasite.

37:21.840 --> 37:23.262
